24
00:02:07,710 --> 00:02:08,349
Hurry!

25
00:02:08,350 --> 00:02:09,509
Search over there!

26
00:02:11,829 --> 00:02:13,069
It's too dangerous.

27
00:02:13,550 --> 00:02:14,669
Go!

28
00:02:15,029 --> 00:02:16,190
Someone's coming.

29
00:02:16,230 --> 00:02:18,150
Since I've found you,

30
00:02:18,509 --> 00:02:20,470
I won't let anyone take you away.

31
00:02:21,830 --> 00:02:23,270
Even if

32
00:02:23,749 --> 00:02:27,270
that person is your imperial father?

33
00:02:28,110 --> 00:02:29,229
