34
00:02:29,870 --> 00:02:30,949
do you know

35
00:02:31,029 --> 00:02:33,150
what's the most ridiculous thing
in this world?

36
00:02:34,589 --> 00:02:37,109
Everyone keeps deciding for me,

37
00:02:38,110 --> 00:02:40,261
yet no one ever asks what I want.

